So you don't

736
00:37:43,570 --> 00:37:44,970
remember your birthday.

737
00:37:45,610 --> 00:37:48,160
♪ United as a song of promise ♪

738
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:48,050
Likewise, I've been a drifter,

739
