755
00:38:14,770 --> 00:38:17,870
♪ Don't ask how long the journey is ♪

756
00:38:18,410 --> 00:38:21,380
♪ What fear is there
if black hair turns to grey? ♪

757
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:22,400
After we get through
these difficult times,

758
